"  lokit auth login --provider custom-openai\n"
"\n"
"Opcja 2: Podaj bezpośrednio:\n"
"  --base-url https://api.example.com/v1"

#: internal/cli/helpers.go:361
msgid ""
"provider 'ollama' requires Ollama server to be running\n"
